1
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:14,480
Didn't you want to be Queen Chu?

2
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:17,480
Haven't you always wanted to replace her?

3
00:00:18,390 --> 00:00:19,850
I'm giving you the chance.

4
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:24,000
Why aren't you taking it?

5
00:00:26,510 --> 00:00:27,030
I...

6
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:29,030
didn't...

7
00:00:38,310 --> 00:00:39,110
Your Majesty,

8
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:42,240
I have nothing but admiration for the bond
between you and Queen Chu,

9
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,640
and no trace of jealousy.

10
00:00:44,430 --> 00:00:45,670
If my death

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,280
could make Queen Chu
change her mind and return to you,

12
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:50,680
I would willingly die before you
right now.

13
00:00:51,670 --> 00:00:53,390
You won't die like this.

14
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Let me tell you...

15
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:57,240
where to stab...

16
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,640
to kill yourself.

17
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,280
Leave!

18
00:01:58,340 --> 00:01:59,289
My Lady.

19
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,050
You are injured?

20
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,430
I'll go get you some medicine.

21
00:02:12,430 --> 00:02:13,290
Leave me alone.

22
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,370
I didn't betray you.

23
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,400
You don't need to pretend to be kind.

24
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,120
Since I agreed to cooperate with you,

25
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,430
I will keep my promise.

26
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,430
You can go back now.

27
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,610
Since it's a cooperation,

28
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,590
it means we share the same goal.

29
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,940
You are not just doing this for me,

30
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:32,910
but also to fulfill your role
as Consort Helian.

31
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,810
You chose this path yourself.

32
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:37,000
From the beginning, you should have known

33
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,329
that life around Yan Xun

34
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:40,200
is not easy.

35
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:49,630
If I hadn't become Consort Helian,

36
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,050
I would already have been

37
00:02:53,050 --> 00:02:56,079
the fourth concubine
of Elder Tubu of Hongchuan Tribe.

38
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,910
I am a daughter of the Helian family.

39
00:02:57,910 --> 00:03:00,470
Helian Tribe is the smallest
among the Great Yan tribes.

40
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,360
This is a fate I cannot change.

41
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,080
Ever since I was born,

42
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:07,040
I knew that all the tribal elders
of Great Yan

43
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:09,960
had their eyes on us,

44
00:03:10,850 --> 00:03:13,850
always wanting to divide
and swallow Helian Tribe.

45
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,090
And my brother...

46
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:22,829
He never once stopped waiting for me
to grow up,

47
00:03:22,829 --> 00:03:23,960
thinking of using me

48
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,310
in exchange for

49
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:27,470
a few horses and grazing lands.

50
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,430
Do you think I had any better choice

51
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:34,520
than becoming Consort Helian?

52
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,430
Even my maids know

53
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:40,760
Yan Xun has never truly spent the night
in my room.

54
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,620
You think I don't know?

55
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:44,400
He just wanted to silence the gossip

56
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,190
by giving me this

57
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:46,920
pitiful and ridiculous title.

58
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:04,490
What are you doing?

59
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:07,190
Don't move.

60
00:04:08,110 --> 00:04:09,310
Your foot is injured.

61
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,610
I'll carry you back.

62
00:05:42,409 --> 00:05:47,650
[REBIRTH]

63
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:50,770
[Episode 19]

64
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,390
Yan Qing,

65
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:56,980
is there any news from the person
we sent to Zhan's Mansion yesterday?

66
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:57,780
Your Majesty,

67
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,720
not yet.

68
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:01,760
But he is still waiting at Zhan's Mansion.

69
00:06:01,890 --> 00:06:03,730
He said that as soon as there's news
about Lord Zhan,

70
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:05,370
he will come to the palace to report.

71
00:06:05,370 --> 00:06:06,490
He went yesterday.

72
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,920
Why is there still no news?

73
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,880
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

74
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,650
Today is the 15th.

75
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,560
His Majesty has been ill for a long time.

76
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,340
The officials are all at Xiangtian Hall,

77
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,540
waiting for you to pray for His Majesty.

78
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:48,540
Recently, His Majesty has been unwell.

79
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:52,720
I will personally pray to the ancestors

80
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,720
to bless him.

81
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:56,610
Xiangtian Hall is a sacred place.

82
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:58,780
You should not disturb it.

83
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:00,630
Yes, Your Majesty.

84
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,370
Ancestors above,

85
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:11,220
may you bless Biantang with peace

86
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,040
and stability for generations,

87
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:16,100
and may our Emperor receive the protection
of his forebears,

88
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:18,100
enjoying long life and good health.

89
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,370
Nobody move!

90
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,190
It's you.

91
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,150
What exactly do you want?

92
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:18,530
Why do you have Zhan Ziyu's jade pendant?

93
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:20,050
Zhan Ziyu is dead.

94
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:22,900
I want to make a deal with you.

95
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,400
You let Li Ce go,

96
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,330
and I will keep your secret.

97
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,020
Let's each take a step back

98
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:29,930
and leave each other a way out.

99
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,320
Why would I need a way out?

100
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:34,610
Zhan Ziyu's identity is not simple.

101
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:37,429
Back then, when the Biantang Emperor
carried out a purge of the Nanxi Tribe,

102
00:08:37,429 --> 00:08:39,559
Zhan Ziyu survived by a stroke of luck.

103
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:40,860
You took him in

104
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:44,650
and used him to train the Nanxi people
as suicide warriors.

105
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:48,270
The assassination attempt in Qinzheng Hall
on His Majesty that day

106
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,790
was your order.

107
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,630
Yesterday,

108
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,600
Zhan Ziyu attempted
to assassinate the Crown Prince

109
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,800
on his way to Youzhou.

110
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,200
It was also your order.

111
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,150
Your Majesty,

112
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:03,510
even though the Biantang Emperor
has favored you for many years,

113
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,390
Li Ce is his only bloodline

114
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:07,450
and the sole heir of Biantang.

115
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:09,510
Why did you attempt
regicide and rebellion?

116
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,900
Once His Majesty recovers,

117
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:12,870
he will eventually realize the truth.

118
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,670
So it's better

119
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,550
to pin all the blame on Lord Zhan

120
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:18,960
before he wakes up to it,

121
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:22,750
so that neither you nor the Crown Prince
will be implicated.

122
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,270
Your Majesty, if you are willing to clear
the Crown Prince's name,

123
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:27,820
I am willing to leave the Crown Prince
from this moment on

124
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:29,280
and take Lord Zhan's place

125
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,220
to work for you.

126
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:37,840
Raising assassins,
attempting to kill His Majesty,

127
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,960
and framing the Crown Prince?

128
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,490
What are you talking about?

129
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:43,620
I don't understand at all.

130
00:09:44,190 --> 00:09:47,190
The Nanxi Tribe was wiped out long ago.

131
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:51,440
Their village back then

132
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:55,270
was burned to the ground years ago.

133
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,880
The Nanxi people have lived by the water
for generations.

134
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:01,480
How could fire alone wipe them out
completely?

135
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,800
The wooden houses they lived in
for generations

136
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:07,150
were located in a valley
backed by the South Mountain.

137
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,960
If the fire was set

138
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,960
in a specific season

139
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,640
and at a specific location,

140
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,410
none of them could escape.

141
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:17,480
Your Majesty,
how do you know this so clearly?

142
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:20,280
The secret imperial order
given to Sun Di back then

143
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,200
was issued by you

144
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,980
personally.

145
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,140
You've said so much.

146
00:10:28,970 --> 00:10:30,230
What proof do you have?

147
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,240
Impossible.

148
00:10:49,970 --> 00:10:52,600
The order to annihilate the Nanxi Tribe
was issued by Biantang Emperor.

149
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,660
It had nothing to do with Her Majesty.

150
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,390
You're just saying this

151
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,680
to make me testify against Her Majesty

152
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:01,190
and admit that it was her
who sent me here.

153
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,010
No matter what you say,

154
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,270
I won't betray her.

155
00:11:04,730 --> 00:11:06,220
Even if you kill me,

156
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:09,750
I won't say a word against her!

157
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,000
Back then,

158
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:14,760
Biantang Emperor sent troops
to wipe out the Nanxi village.

159
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,490
But after several deployments,

160
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:19,020
they still couldn't
defeat them completely.

161
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:21,490
The Empress,
in order to please her husband,

162
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,460
went to great lengths

163
00:11:23,930 --> 00:11:24,800
and finally found a way

164
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,870
to wipe out the Nanxi Tribe

165
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,550
by exploiting the unique structure

166
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:30,390
and terrain of their settlements

167
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,250
to set the entire village on fire.

168
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:43,870
Zhen,

169
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:46,750
tell me this isn't true.

170
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,960
This isn't true.

171
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,280
Run!

172
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:05,750
Ziming!

173
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:06,670
Ziming!

174
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:19,480
Don't run!

175
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:23,480
Stop!

176
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,540
A remnant of the Nanxi Tribe?

177
00:12:32,540 --> 00:12:34,340
How dare you offend the Empress?

178
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:35,730
Step back.

179
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,390
This is for you.

180
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:06,870
Are you hungry?

181
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:44,560
This...

182
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:46,220
Your Majesty.

183
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,560
What are you doing?

184
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:50,350
Princess Fu!

185
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:54,030
Do you know that holding the Empress hostage
is a crime of treason?

186
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,400
Step back, all of you!

187
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,100
This is a crime of treason!

188
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,230
Raising assassins,

189
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:00,620
attempting to assassinate His Majesty,

190
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:02,010
and framing the Crown Prince

191
00:14:02,010 --> 00:14:03,540
are also crimes of treason.

192
00:14:04,170 --> 00:14:04,770
Move!

193
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:07,500
This...

194
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:16,650
Everyone, step back!

195
00:14:16,650 --> 00:14:17,250
Step back!

196
00:14:19,410 --> 00:14:20,290
Zhan Ziyu,

197
00:14:20,860 --> 00:14:22,010
tell everyone here,

198
00:14:22,310 --> 00:14:23,170
who ordered you

199
00:14:23,650 --> 00:14:26,010
to use assassins to kill His Majesty

200
00:14:26,300 --> 00:14:27,690
and frame the Crown Prince?

201
00:14:27,690 --> 00:14:28,750
And who ordered you

202
00:14:28,890 --> 00:14:30,980
to eliminate the Crown Prince

203
00:14:31,290 --> 00:14:33,140
on his way to Youzhou?

204
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:33,930
Speak!

205
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:40,290
Zhan Ziyu,

206
00:14:41,090 --> 00:14:43,220
I don't understand what she's saying.

207
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:47,260
Can you explain it to me?

208
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,410
Do you remember

209
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,690
the scene when you brought me back

210
00:14:52,690 --> 00:14:54,580
from the destroyed village in Nanxi

211
00:14:54,580 --> 00:14:55,890
15 years ago?

212
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:56,620
Nanxi?

213
00:14:57,290 --> 00:14:58,690
Zhan Ziyu is from Nanxi?

214
00:14:59,050 --> 00:15:00,010
Nanxi?

215
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:02,730
The sky that day

216
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:04,930
was as bright as today.

217
00:15:08,090 --> 00:15:09,660
Looking at your face,

218
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:11,530
I secretly swore that

219
00:15:12,170 --> 00:15:15,740
I, Zhan Ziyu,

220
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,500
would only have one woman in my heart,

221
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:20,200
live only for her,

222
00:15:20,930 --> 00:15:23,130
and love only her for the rest of my life.

223
00:15:23,410 --> 00:15:24,770
That is you.

224
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:26,500
It's...

225
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,740
What a scandal!

226
00:15:27,770 --> 00:15:28,970
Because of this oath,

227
00:15:29,290 --> 00:15:30,460
I would do whatever

228
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,260
you want me to do.

229
00:15:33,170 --> 00:15:34,580
As long as it's your wish,

230
00:15:35,050 --> 00:15:36,740
I could even give up my life,

231
00:15:37,530 --> 00:15:38,620
let alone bear the mere charge

232
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:40,530
of assassinating His Majesty.

233
00:15:41,690 --> 00:15:44,930
But do you know my wish?

234
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:51,140
I want to talk to Her Majesty alone.

235
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:55,770
Step back!

236
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,010
Nobody move!

237
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:10,600
For the past fifteen years,

238
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:15,740
I could only hide in the dark

239
00:16:19,210 --> 00:16:22,090
and peep at you in the corner.

240
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:24,500
Your Majesty...

241
00:16:26,990 --> 00:16:30,350
The sunlight that day
was as warm as it is today.

242
00:16:36,050 --> 00:16:37,050
This...

243
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:43,510
The seasons are out of order,

244
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:45,250
and the universe is reversed!

245
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:48,140
It's an ominous sign!

246
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:49,810
What should we do?

247
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:29,830
Zhen...

248
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:33,890
I can no longer serve you.

249
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,730
Are you hungry?

250
00:18:18,060 --> 00:18:19,490
Guards! Protect me!

251
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:20,560
Don't move!

252
00:18:21,170 --> 00:18:22,930
Chu Qiao, a famale slave from Great Yong,

253
00:18:22,930 --> 00:18:25,540
conspired with a remnant
of the Nanxi Tribe, Zhan Ziyu,

254
00:18:25,540 --> 00:18:27,140
to frame me!

255
00:18:27,810 --> 00:18:29,140
Arrest them all!

256
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:38,780
Stop!

257
00:18:40,490 --> 00:18:41,170
Minglu!

258
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:44,500
They are all accomplices
of Crown Prince Li Ce!

259
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:45,620
Show no mercy!

260
00:18:45,890 --> 00:18:47,970
Kill them,
and I will reward you handsomely!

261
00:18:47,970 --> 00:18:49,340
Bad news! Bad news!

262
00:18:49,340 --> 00:18:50,210
Something happened to His Majesty!

263
00:18:50,210 --> 00:18:53,730
An assassin broke into Zhengyuan Hall
and took His Majesty hostage.

264
00:18:53,730 --> 00:18:54,410
What...

265
00:18:54,410 --> 00:18:55,730
What should we do?

266
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:56,670
Take them away!

267
00:19:08,780 --> 00:19:09,580
Your Majesty!

268
00:19:40,170 --> 00:19:40,970
Your Majesty!

269
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:46,730
Who are you

270
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,920
to dare hold His Majesty hostage?

271
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,690
You don't need to know who I am.

272
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:53,280
Release Princess Fu and her people now.

273
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:56,070
Then, in front of all the officials,
announce

274
00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:59,040
that you ordered Zhan Ziyu to attempt
to assassinate His Majesty

275
00:19:59,040 --> 00:20:01,110
and frame Crown Prince Li Ce,

276
00:20:01,130 --> 00:20:02,260
and I will let him go.

277
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:05,210
Empress,

278
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:06,890
save me!

279
00:20:07,850 --> 00:20:08,970
Hurry up and release Chu Qiao
and the others,

280
00:20:08,970 --> 00:20:10,250
and admit that you did it.

281
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,490
I won't believe it.

282
00:20:11,860 --> 00:20:13,820
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

283
00:20:13,850 --> 00:20:16,000
Saving His Majesty is the priority,
Your Majesty.

284
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:16,630
Yes!

285
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:18,520
Saving His Majesty is the priority!

286
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:19,650
Audacious traitor!

287
00:20:20,060 --> 00:20:21,410
To frame me,

288
00:20:21,690 --> 00:20:25,090
you actually dare to hold His Majesty hostage
to threaten me.

289
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,620
Who ordered you?

290
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,600
The Crown Prince or Chu Qiao?

291
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:32,070
Empress,
are you really going to save yourself

292
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:34,020
at the cost of the Emperor's life?

293
00:20:34,020 --> 00:20:36,350
Of course I care about His Majesty's life.

294
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:38,020
That is exactly why I will not negotiate

295
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:39,780
with rebels and traitors.

296
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,060
Guards!

297
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:43,890
Kill the traitor
and take His Majesty back!

298
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:45,890
Your Majesty!

299
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:47,260
Do it now!

300
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:50,900
Your Majesty!

301
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:53,970
Your Majesty!

302
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:55,390
Your Majesty!

303
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:25,270
Your Majesty!

304
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,420
Your Majesty!

305
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:46,380
I am here!

306
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:47,920
Anyone who makes a move

307
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:50,290
will be punished for rebellion!

308
00:21:55,930 --> 00:21:56,540
Father!

309
00:22:11,560 --> 00:22:12,860
Your Majesty!

310
00:22:15,170 --> 00:22:16,670
I have come by your imperial order

311
00:22:16,670 --> 00:22:17,590
to protect you!

312
00:22:44,060 --> 00:22:44,780
Good.

313
00:22:46,120 --> 00:22:48,120
I have tolerated you for many years,

314
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:50,070
thinking you knew your limits.

315
00:22:51,010 --> 00:22:54,640
I never expected that you would not only
move against the Crown Prince,

316
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:56,600
but also come after me.

317
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:58,860
Stop acting.

318
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:03,000
You are selfish, hypocritical,
and always putting on an act.

319
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:04,690
To me,

320
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:07,840
to your own brother Crown Prince Maocheng,

321
00:23:08,690 --> 00:23:11,620
and to your people and ministers alike.

322
00:23:12,930 --> 00:23:14,140
You deceived me,

323
00:23:14,650 --> 00:23:16,020
went back on your word,

324
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:19,650
and killed my child,

325
00:23:19,980 --> 00:23:21,710
yet still pretended to love me.

326
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:22,730
For the throne,

327
00:23:22,730 --> 00:23:24,590
you even killed your own brother!

328
00:23:25,140 --> 00:23:26,730
You feign mourning him.

329
00:23:26,890 --> 00:23:29,020
Going out of the palace to pray for him?

330
00:23:29,330 --> 00:23:31,130
Your acting is so convincing...

331
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:34,280
you've almost convinced yourself.

332
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:36,780
If only you knew nothing

333
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:39,780
and were a little more foolish.

334
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,570
Perhaps I could continue to favor you

335
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:45,220
and play this game with you forever.

336
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:53,970
You shouldn't have seen through me,

337
00:23:53,970 --> 00:23:56,570
and you absolutely
shouldn't have exposed me.

338
00:23:56,970 --> 00:23:58,970
You should have kept playing along.

339
00:24:01,540 --> 00:24:03,170
Did it have to come to this?

340
00:24:04,730 --> 00:24:07,170
Is the favor I gave you not enough?

341
00:24:16,650 --> 00:24:18,060
Don't be afraid.

342
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:20,490
I never intended to kill you.

343
00:24:21,140 --> 00:24:23,730
Because I never wanted to die with you.

344
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:25,490
In this life,

345
00:24:26,170 --> 00:24:28,410
in heaven or in hell,

346
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:30,720
I never want to see you again.

347
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:34,650
This world—

348
00:24:39,950 --> 00:24:41,180
I don't want it.

349
00:24:43,730 --> 00:24:44,660
Your Majesty...

350
00:24:58,910 --> 00:25:00,040
Your Majesty!

351
00:25:28,450 --> 00:25:29,020
Ce!

352
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:11,720
Zhen.

353
00:26:22,330 --> 00:26:24,330
The sunshine is so beautiful today.

354
00:27:07,650 --> 00:27:08,220
How is he?

355
00:27:08,250 --> 00:27:10,060
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

356
00:27:10,060 --> 00:27:11,890
His Majesty has a pre-existing condition.

357
00:27:11,890 --> 00:27:13,700
Coupled with years of excess
and lack of restraint,

358
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:15,190
he was already critically ill.

359
00:27:15,190 --> 00:27:16,190
This incident

360
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:18,170
has completely drained his vitality.

361
00:27:18,170 --> 00:27:18,970
I'm afraid...

362
00:27:19,210 --> 00:27:21,270
I'm afraid there will be no recovery.

363
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:28,880
Your Highness,

364
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:31,350
His Majesty has been unwell for many days,

365
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:33,610
but a nation cannot be without a ruler
even for a single day.

366
00:27:33,610 --> 00:27:35,930
Please make preparations

367
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:37,420
in advance.

368
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:47,240
Please make preparations in advance,
Your Highness.

369
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:11,100
Mother,

370
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:14,320
Father is very ill.

371
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:16,690
After what you did,

372
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:20,230
he likely does not have many days left.

373
00:28:20,540 --> 00:28:22,670
I know you don't want to be with Father,

374
00:28:23,620 --> 00:28:25,280
so I overruled all objections

375
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,740
and insisted on burying you here.

376
00:28:28,490 --> 00:28:30,100
You will not see him again.

377
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:33,330
I know you do not want me to come see you,

378
00:28:33,850 --> 00:28:35,540
but I did not come empty-handed.

379
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:37,870
I brought your favorite green rice balls.

380
00:28:51,210 --> 00:28:52,170
Mother!

381
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:54,620
Mother!

382
00:28:58,410 --> 00:28:59,060
Mother,

383
00:28:59,590 --> 00:29:02,040
do you like the flower I picked for you?

384
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:04,500
I'll put it in your hair.

385
00:29:17,970 --> 00:29:18,650
Mother,

386
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:20,410
if you don't like it,

387
00:29:21,580 --> 00:29:23,890
I won't do it again.

388
00:29:28,040 --> 00:29:28,630
Ce.

389
00:29:43,580 --> 00:29:45,910
These are your favorite green rice balls.

390
00:29:48,650 --> 00:29:49,890
I know you

391
00:29:50,300 --> 00:29:51,620
had never loved me.

392
00:29:52,570 --> 00:29:54,490
And I know you despised me.

393
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,680
You didn't even want to touch me.

394
00:29:57,890 --> 00:29:58,690
I even know that you

395
00:29:58,690 --> 00:30:00,890
wanted to cut me into a thousand pieces.

396
00:30:02,250 --> 00:30:04,530
But in the dead of night,

397
00:30:05,300 --> 00:30:07,700
I still fantasize
about lying in your arms,

398
00:30:07,970 --> 00:30:09,650
listening to your stories.

399
00:30:10,780 --> 00:30:12,040
Fantasizing about...

400
00:30:13,340 --> 00:30:15,060
falling asleep

401
00:30:16,450 --> 00:30:17,650
to your lullabies

402
00:30:19,690 --> 00:30:21,150
and never waking up again.

403
00:30:30,890 --> 00:30:33,500
His Majesty has arrived!

404
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:59,690
Li Yan, the legitimate son
of the late Prince of Chang, Heir Luo,

405
00:30:59,690 --> 00:31:00,970
has inherited generations
of loyalty and bravery

406
00:31:00,970 --> 00:31:02,730
and is both virtuous and capable.

407
00:31:02,730 --> 00:31:04,930
He is hereby enfeoffed as Prince of Luo.

408
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:06,380
He is granted a python robe,

409
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:09,420
1,000 qing of estate land, 300 houses,

410
00:31:09,450 --> 00:31:13,160
500 bolts of fine silk,
and 100 fine horses.

411
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:16,170
Thank you, Your Majesty.

412
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:28,160
Prince of Luo.

413
00:31:34,950 --> 00:31:35,660
Leave us.

414
00:31:38,850 --> 00:31:41,640
Truly, one cannot judge by appearance.
You have hidden your strength well.

415
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:44,640
I did not expect you
to be so calculating and scheming.

416
00:31:46,330 --> 00:31:47,740
If I remember correctly,

417
00:31:48,250 --> 00:31:49,140
the palace prayer ceremony
on the 15th of each month

418
00:31:49,140 --> 00:31:51,480
is handled by the Ministry of Rites.

419
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:53,170
If it were not for you, Minister of Rites,

420
00:31:53,170 --> 00:31:54,490
making things convenient for Chu Qiao,

421
00:31:54,490 --> 00:31:55,450
how could she have appeared

422
00:31:55,450 --> 00:31:56,850
in Youtian Hall that day?

423
00:32:10,930 --> 00:32:12,730
So you betrayed your allegiance

424
00:32:12,980 --> 00:32:14,180
just for a stupid robe

425
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,350
and a few shabby houses?

426
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:34,100
Prince of Luo, wearing this python robe
that brings you honor,

427
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:35,790
you really do look every bit the refined

428
00:32:35,790 --> 00:32:37,750
and upright gentleman.

429
00:32:46,690 --> 00:32:47,340
Chunxing!

430
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:48,540
Pack my things!

431
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:49,760
I'm going back to Great Yong.

432
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,350
Chun'er!

433
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:56,410
Why aren't you packing?

434
00:32:56,410 --> 00:32:58,350
Your Highness,
please don't speak in anger.

435
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,540
Now that His Highness has been enfeoffed,

436
00:32:59,540 --> 00:33:00,960
you will be a princess consort.

437
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:01,820
In all of Biantang,

438
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,220
no one will dare bully...

439
00:33:06,270 --> 00:33:06,930
Let go of me!

440
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:08,810
You're hurting me!

441
00:33:19,570 --> 00:33:21,700
You're acting tough in front of me now,

442
00:33:21,870 --> 00:33:22,890
but in front of Chu Qiao and Li Ce,

443
00:33:22,890 --> 00:33:24,090
you're just a coward!

444
00:33:24,410 --> 00:33:25,810
I can't stand it anymore.

445
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:28,380
I'm going back to Great Yong
to find Zhao Che!

446
00:33:29,430 --> 00:33:30,410
Let go! Let go of me!

447
00:33:30,410 --> 00:33:31,690
Zhao Chun'er, enough!

448
00:33:31,690 --> 00:33:32,730
Let me go!

449
00:33:33,210 --> 00:33:34,210
Don't be naive!

450
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:35,580
Do you think your Zhao Che

451
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:36,710
will still want you?

452
00:33:37,170 --> 00:33:38,610
We've been married for days.

453
00:33:38,610 --> 00:33:40,740
Has he ever sent anyone to check on you?

454
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:42,410
Your title as Princess

455
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:43,780
is just a toy he gave you

456
00:33:43,780 --> 00:33:45,730
to placate a child.

457
00:33:47,490 --> 00:33:48,340
Let go!

458
00:33:49,690 --> 00:33:50,970
Listen to me!

459
00:33:51,620 --> 00:33:53,450
You're not allowed to go anywhere!

460
00:33:53,450 --> 00:33:54,970
Just stay in the mansion.

461
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:59,620
You, a deposed princess,

462
00:34:00,100 --> 00:34:02,170
and I, a useless prince,

463
00:34:02,690 --> 00:34:04,540
are a match made in heaven.

464
00:34:05,330 --> 00:34:08,090
I will achieve every single thing

465
00:34:08,850 --> 00:34:10,170
I promised you!

466
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:17,540
Keep an eye on her.

467
00:34:17,850 --> 00:34:19,810
Don't let her leave this room.

468
00:34:20,500 --> 00:34:21,100
Yes.

469
00:35:01,730 --> 00:35:03,460
I thought you were smart.

470
00:35:04,330 --> 00:35:06,690
I didn't expect you to be so stupid too.

471
00:35:07,060 --> 00:35:08,900
Don't stop me! Let me die!

472
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:11,730
Let go of me! Let go of me!

473
00:35:17,250 --> 00:35:18,450
Why do you want to die?

474
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:19,930
Is it for the Empress,

475
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,290
or Zhan Ziyu?

476
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,020
I...

477
00:35:33,690 --> 00:35:35,460
After the Nanxi Tribe was wiped out,

478
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:37,200
you were separated from Zhan Ziyu

479
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,460
and sold into slavery.

480
00:35:39,330 --> 00:35:40,930
It took him years to find you.

481
00:35:41,690 --> 00:35:42,690
You were a slave.

482
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:44,190
You should know

483
00:35:44,620 --> 00:35:45,770
the life you're living now

484
00:35:45,770 --> 00:35:47,770
is thousands of times better than before.

485
00:35:47,770 --> 00:35:49,500
You survived back then.

486
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:51,400
But now you want to die?

487
00:35:51,770 --> 00:35:53,060
Isn't that too stupid?

488
00:35:53,650 --> 00:35:55,850
Ziyu is my only family

489
00:35:55,850 --> 00:35:56,970
in this world.

490
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:59,620
My clansmen were killed by the Empress.

491
00:35:59,720 --> 00:36:02,120
Even my only family is dead.

492
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,530
What's the point of living?

493
00:36:18,290 --> 00:36:19,580
The child in your womb

494
00:36:19,790 --> 00:36:21,310
is your only family.

495
00:36:21,850 --> 00:36:23,020
The child?

496
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:25,420
Although Zhan Ziyu is your brother,

497
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:26,900
he exploited your youth

498
00:36:27,450 --> 00:36:28,780
to work for the Empress.

499
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,440
You are so smart.

500
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:36,370
And Li Ce is a kind

501
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:37,780
and affectionate man.

502
00:36:38,470 --> 00:36:40,330
Now he is the Emperor of Biantang,

503
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:43,900
and you are carrying his only child.

504
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:47,280
Think about it carefully.

505
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:28,980
These two swords

506
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:30,090
represent

507
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,980
that we will be together forever.

508
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:33,360
What my mother lost,

509
00:37:33,770 --> 00:37:35,690
I'll win back for her.

510
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:36,980
Kill this witch!

511
00:37:36,980 --> 00:37:38,800
If we offer her to the King of Great Yan,

512
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:40,070
we'll be saved.

513
00:37:40,370 --> 00:37:41,250
Catch her!

514
00:37:41,250 --> 00:37:42,500
Set off!

515
00:37:43,210 --> 00:37:44,620
Long live Great Yan!

516
00:37:44,650 --> 00:37:46,170
Crush Biantang!

